snippet.title: Morels: The Hunt 2- Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Coming to Playstation 5 Soon! https://store.playstation.com/en-us/concept/10011360

Morels: The Hunt 2 is Available Now on Steam! https://store.steampowered.com/app/2686250/Morels_The_Hunt_2

Morels: The Hunt 2 is a simulation game about mushroom hunting and wildlife photography. Explore a diverse range of locations spanning across the globe. Increase your hunter and photographer levels by collecting a variety of mushrooms, photographing animals, and completing weekly tasks.

Experience all new maps, animals, mushrooms, insects and objects to photograph, new shop items, weekly tasks, and more.
